{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 3,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 359.985,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.483,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, returned from speaking with the Lord,",
      "verse": "3:1",
      "lineIndex": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 3.663,
      "end": 5.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the tent of my father.",
      "verse": "3:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.968,
      "end": 8.244,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then he spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.424,
      "end": 10.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold I have dreamed a dream,",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.88,
      "end": 13.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the which the Lord has commanded me",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.475,
      "end": 16.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that you and your brothers shall return to Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.452,
      "end": 20.238,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, Laban has the record of the Jews",
      "verse": "3:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.418,
      "end": 23.204,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also a genealogy of my forefathers,",
      "verse": "3:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 23.384,
      "end": 26.124,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are engraved upon plates of brass.",
      "verse": "3:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 26.804,
      "end": 28.708,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, the Lord has commanded me",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 28.888,
      "end": 32.464,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that you and your brothers should go to the house of Laban,",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 32.644,
      "end": 34.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and seek the records,",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 34.31,
      "end": 36.911,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring them down here into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 37.591,
      "end": 40.052,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, behold your brothers complain,",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 40.232,
      "end": 43.761,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saying it is a hard thing which I have required of them;",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 43.941,
      "end": 46.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold I have not required it of them,",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 46.629,
      "end": 49.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but it is a commandment of the Lord.",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 49.956,
      "end": 51.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore go, my son,",
      "verse": "3:6",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 51.669,
      "end": 54.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you shall be favored of the Lord,",
      "verse": "3:6",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 54.217,
      "end": 56.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because you have not complained.",
      "verse": "3:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 56.987,
      "end": 59.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, said to my father:",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 59.489,
      "end": 63.158,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will go and do the things which the Lord has commanded,",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 63.338,
      "end": 67.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that the Lord gives no commandments to the children of men,",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 67.605,
      "end": 70.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save he shall prepare a way for them",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 70.386,
      "end": 74.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may accomplish the thing which he commands them.",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 74.688,
      "end": 77.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when my father had heard these words",
      "verse": "3:8",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 77.329,
      "end": 78.769,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was very glad,",
      "verse": "3:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 78.949,
      "end": 81.968,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he knew that I had been blessed of the Lord.",
      "verse": "3:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 82.648,
      "end": 86.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, and my brothers took our journey in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "3:9",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 87.054,
      "end": 88.633,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with our tents,",
      "verse": "3:9",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 88.813,
      "end": 90.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to go up to the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "3:9",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 91.583,
      "end": 94.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when we had gone up to the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "3:10",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 94.874,
      "end": 97.614,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I and my brothers consulted one with another.",
      "verse": "3:10",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 98.294,
      "end": 99.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we cast lots\u2014",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 99.728,
      "end": 102.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who of us should go in to the house of Laban.",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 102.462,
      "end": 104.738,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the lot fell upon Laman;",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 104.918,
      "end": 107.519,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Laman went in to the house of Laban,",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 107.699,
      "end": 110.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he talked with him as he sat in his house.",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 111.537,
      "end": 114.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he desired of Laban the records",
      "verse": "3:12",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 114.364,
      "end": 117.383,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraved upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "3:12",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 117.563,
      "end": 120.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which contained the genealogy of my father.",
      "verse": "3:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 121.169,
      "end": 123.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, then Laban was angry,",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 123.81,
      "end": 126.086,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thrust him out from his presence;",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 126.266,
      "end": 129.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he would not that he should have the records.",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 129.65,
      "end": 131.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, he said to him:",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 131.502,
      "end": 134.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold you are a robber, and I will kill you.",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 134.829,
      "end": 137.244,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But Laman fled out of his presence,",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 137.424,
      "end": 140.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and told the things which Laban had done, to us.",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 140.762,
      "end": 142.991,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we began to be very sorrowful,",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 143.171,
      "end": 147.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my brothers were about to return to my father in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 147.752,
      "end": 149.981,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold I said to them that:",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 150.161,
      "end": 151.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "As the Lord lives,",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 151.641,
      "end": 153.081,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as we live,",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 153.261,
      "end": 156.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we will not go down to our father in the wilderness",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 157.156,
      "end": 160.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until we have accomplished the thing which the Lord has commanded us.",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 161.505,
      "end": 163.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, let us be faithful",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 163.31,
      "end": 165.493,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in keeping the commandments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 165.673,
      "end": 170.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore let us go down to the land of our father's inheritance,",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 170.265,
      "end": 172.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold he left gold and silver,",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 172.721,
      "end": 174.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all manner of riches.",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 174.666,
      "end": 178.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all this he has done because of the commandments of the Lord.",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 179.247,
      "end": 181.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he knew that Jerusalem must be destroyed,",
      "verse": "3:17",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 182.167,
      "end": 184.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the wickedness of the people.",
      "verse": "3:17",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 185.076,
      "end": 188.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, they have rejected the words of the prophets.",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 188.321,
      "end": 190.643,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, if my father should dwell in the land",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 190.823,
      "end": 193.934,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after he has been commanded to flee out of the land,",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 194.114,
      "end": 196.343,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he would also perish.",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 196.523,
      "end": 199.82,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, it must needs be that he flee out of the land.",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 200.5,
      "end": 205.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, it is wisdom in God that we should obtain these records,",
      "verse": "3:19",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 205.788,
      "end": 210.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we may preserve to our children the language of our fathers;",
      "verse": "3:19",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 210.694,
      "end": 213.852,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also that we may preserve to them the words",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 214.032,
      "end": 217.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been spoken by the mouth of all the holy prophets,",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 217.602,
      "end": 221.967,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been delivered to them by the Spirit and power of God,",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 222.147,
      "end": 223.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "since the world began,",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 223.999,
      "end": 225.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even down to this present time.",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 226.537,
      "end": 229.927,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after this manner of language did I persuade my brothers,",
      "verse": "3:21",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 230.107,
      "end": 233.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they might be faithful in keeping the commandments of God.",
      "verse": "3:21",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 234.363,
      "end": 237.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then we went down to the land of our inheritance,",
      "verse": "3:22",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 237.747,
      "end": 240.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we gathered together our gold, and our silver,",
      "verse": "3:22",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 240.992,
      "end": 242.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our precious things.",
      "verse": "3:22",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 243.297,
      "end": 245.944,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had gathered these things together,",
      "verse": "3:23",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 246.124,
      "end": 248.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we went up again to the house of Laban.",
      "verse": "3:23",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 249.033,
      "end": 252.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then we went in to Laban, and desired him",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 252.417,
      "end": 254.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would give to us the records",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 255.151,
      "end": 258.17,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraved upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 258.35,
      "end": 261.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for which we would give to him our gold, and our silver,",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 262.106,
      "end": 263.964,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all our precious things.",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 264.644,
      "end": 267.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then when Laban saw our property,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 267.425,
      "end": 270.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that it was very great, he did desire it,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 270.577,
      "end": 272.945,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that he thrust us out,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 273.125,
      "end": 275.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and sent his servants to kill us,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 275.395,
      "end": 277.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might obtain our property.",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 278.304,
      "end": 281.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then we fled before the servants of Laban,",
      "verse": "3:26",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 281.363,
      "end": 284.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we were obliged to leave behind our property,",
      "verse": "3:26",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 284.84,
      "end": 287.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it fell into the hands of Laban.",
      "verse": "3:26",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 287.888,
      "end": 290.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then we fled into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "3:27",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 290.529,
      "end": 293.687,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the servants of Laban did not overtake us,",
      "verse": "3:27",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 293.867,
      "end": 296.607,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we hid ourselves in the cavity of a rock.",
      "verse": "3:27",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 297.287,
      "end": 299.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then Laman was angry with me,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 299.743,
      "end": 301.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also with my father;",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 301.641,
      "end": 303.359,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also was Lemuel,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 303.539,
      "end": 306.047,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he listened to the words of Laman.",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 306.227,
      "end": 309.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So Laman and Lemuel spoke many hard words to us,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 309.936,
      "end": 311.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their younger brothers,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 311.695,
      "end": 314.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they struck us even with a rod.",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 314.79,
      "end": 317.205,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then as they struck us with a rod,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 317.385,
      "end": 320.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, an angel of the Lord came and stood before them,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 320.955,
      "end": 322.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he spoke to them, saying:",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 322.993,
      "end": 326.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Why do you strike your younger brother with a rod?",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 326.192,
      "end": 330.186,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know you not that the Lord has chosen him to be a ruler over you,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 330.366,
      "end": 332.688,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and this because of your iniquities?",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 332.868,
      "end": 335.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold you shall go up to Jerusalem again,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 335.695,
      "end": 338.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lord will deliver Laban into your hands.",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 339.161,
      "end": 342.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the angel had spoken to us, he departed.",
      "verse": "3:30",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 342.86,
      "end": 345.089,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the angel had departed,",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 345.269,
      "end": 348.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Laman and Lemuel again began to complain, saying:",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 348.514,
      "end": 352.369,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it possible that the Lord will deliver Laban into our hands?",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 352.549,
      "end": 355.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, he is a mighty man, and he can command fifty,",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 356.073,
      "end": 359.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even he can kill fifty; then why not us?",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 124
    }
  ]
}